Conditional statement :- if, else, elif
valid for vote or not

age = 18
if (age>= 18):
    print("valid for vote")
else:
    print("not vaild")
------------------------------------
traffice light example

light = input("enter the light color:") 

if (light == "green"):
    print("go")

elif(light == "red"):
    print("stop")

elif(light == "yellow"):
    print("wait")
else:
    print("light is broken")

---------------------------------------------------
Grading system in school
marks = int(input("enter the marks: "))

if (marks >= 90):
    print("grade A")
elif(marks >= 80 and marks <90 ):
    print("grade B")

elif(marks >= 70 and marks < 80):
    print("grade c")
elif (marks >=60 and marks <70):
    print("grade D")

else: 
    print("fail Saala")
